{"tid":2376446,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關“自殘”的探討","createTime":"2021-01-22T21:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T10:34:12.000Z","uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba4bf9d16e9ee25ae48f643179d98d80c5d0787","tid":2376446,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:21:18.000Z","msg":"一種刑具名為&quot;立枷&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.easyatm.com.tw/wiki/%E7%AB%8B%E6%9E%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.easyatm.com.tw%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259E%25B7&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5Ab0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=de7bc122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.easyatm.com.tw/wiki/%E7%AB%8B%E6%9E%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n當受刑者坐下，就會窒息，因此必須晝夜站著才能保持性命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果受刑者自行選擇坐下，是不是&ldquo;自殘&rdquo;呢？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;無形立枷&rdquo;在世界到處存在，而在末期資本主義社會，&ldquo;無形立枷&rdquo;更加是無處不在<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;無刑立枷&rdquo;也衍生出兩種特別概念，<br />\n分別是&ldquo;自殘&rdquo;（坐下），同&ldquo;心甘情願&rdquo;（站着）"},{"pid":"d8c680d51309b26a26ac175f8b768c0f51f565cf","tid":2376446,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:37:22.000Z","msg":"資本主義走到末期，&ldquo;無形之手&rdquo;會腐化，取而代之的是&ldquo;無形立枷&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n末期資本主義社會再接近末期，&ldquo;無形立枷&rdquo;就再衍生出更複雜的概念，無論受刑者坐下，抑或站着，都是&ldquo;心甘情願去自殘&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9bea2954fc414a3a9ae915758c6dabbde76e80cd","tid":2376446,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8c680d51309b26a26ac175f8b768c0f51f565cf","tid":2376446,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:37:22.000Z","msg":"資本主義走到末期，&ldquo;無形之手&rdquo;會腐化，取而代之的是&ldquo;無形立枷&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n末期資本主義社會再接近末期，&ldquo;無形立枷&rdquo;就再衍生出更複雜的概念，無論受刑者坐下，抑或站着，都是&ldquo;心甘情願去自殘&rdquo;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T21:49:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cZGwaoLA4bI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcZGwaoLA4bI&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5Ab0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=25ba7c26\" da